    host -->|"read/write namespaced state [via Repository]"| repo
    host -->|"read/write confined files [fs capability]"| pstore
    host -->|"publishes derived event [via event.Bus]"| evt
    repo -->|"backed by [SQL]"| db
    evt -->|"backed by [NATS]"| bus

